# Per-SKU reference profile images live here at runtime.
#
# Convention:  store-data/reference-images/{shop_id}/{barcode}.jpg
#
#   - One image per SKU (barcode), captured once at first stock intake and
#     reused for every unit of that SKU.
#   - Scoped per shop_id so the same barcode can carry different packaging
#     across stores and never leaks between tenants.
#   - The inventory row links to it via products.reference_image_path.
#
# The actual .jpg files are git-ignored (see .gitignore); this .gitkeep only
# preserves the directory + documents the convention in the repo.
